text: Dubai chocolate is a chocolate bar with a filling made of kadaif and pistachio. It was first created by Fix Dessert Chocolatier in Dubai in 2021, branded as Can't Get Knafeh of It. The product was popularized in 2024 after being promoted by influencers on social media, especially TikTok. == Related pages == * Ruby chocolate Category:Dubai Category:Chocolate bars
